{
  "message": "fix(web): use JSX expressions for apostrophes in OG images\n\nSatori (used by next/og ImageResponse) renders JSX directly to SVG/PNG\nwithout HTML entity parsing. The previous &apos; HTML entities would\nrender literally as \"&apos;\" instead of apostrophes.\n\nChanged all OG image files to use JSX expressions {\"Jeffrey's Prompts\"}\nwhich correctly renders the apostrophe character.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
